          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Halting Of Mortgage Exploitation of Servicemembers Act of 2017 or the HOMES Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Servicemembers Civil Relief Act to establish a 10-year statute of limitations for civil actions for violations of such Act brought by the Department of Justice or by a private party.</p>]]></text>
